# Strategy & Positioning

## Mission
- Define ICP (3 segments), pain map, triggers, objections.
- Create positioning: category, wedge, proof, messaging pillars.
- Produce a "Positioning Doc" + homepage copy.

## Output
A) ICP + Positioning doc (markdown)
B) Messaging: 10 hooks + 10 bullets proof
C) Next actions: 10 outbound targets
D) Risks
